{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Let\u2019s Get Larry a Haircut</strong> is a <strong>2D block-pushing puzzle game</strong> in which you must navigate and manipulate objects in a maze collecting enough tokens to unlock the hairdressing place, then push Larry in there. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With block-pushing and sokoban style gameplay inspired by games like Repton, Boulder Dash and the like, Larry is a relaxing game about not getting crushed or blowing up the wrong things.\u00a0Also, don\u2019t telefrag Larry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334830/extras/Larry-cow.gif?t=1738676911\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Pros:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lots of puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Catchy music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It has Bees</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You control a sort of 2D cow face</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are time and fewest steps challenges if you like that sort of thing</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Cons:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You control a sort of 2D cow face</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not a very realistic depiction of getting haircuts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In fact there's no actual hairdressing action whatsoever</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334830/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738676911","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334830/page.bg.jpg?t=1738676911","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334830/aac2eb3ffdc5200156d50efbf7d6a0601b99b224/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738676911","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.a